{"tid":2208433,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【港人送中第 27 天】家屬委託律師任全牛再被拒見當事人　已正式申請將當事人移送香港","createTime":"2020-09-19T02:10:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T02:15:16.000Z","uid":54337,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ee342cd19326958082d2480a9e4eea17a103e9ee","tid":2208433,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:10:37.000Z","msg":"【港人送中第 27 天】家屬委託律師任全牛再被拒見當事人 已正式申請將當事人移送香港<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%AC%AC-27-%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%A7%94%E8%A8%97%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%9B%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E8%A6%8B%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%B0%87%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AC%25AC-27-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25A7%2594%25E8%25A8%2597%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=22a137ce\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2580%2581%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E7%25AC%25AC-27-%25E5%25A4%25A9-%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E5%25B1%25AC%25E5%25A7%2594%25E8%25A8%2597%25E5%25BE%258B%25E5%25B8%25AB%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2589%259B%25E5%2586%258D%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25A6%258B%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E5%25BC%258F%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%25E5%25B0%2587%25E7%2595%25B6%25E4%25BA%258B%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%25A7%25BB%25E9%2580%2581%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%2F&h=be635859\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E9%80%81%E4%B8%AD%E7%AC%AC-27-%E5%A4%A9-%E5%AE%B6%E5%B1%AC%E5%A7%94%E8%A8%97%E5%BE%8B%E5%B8%AB%E4%BB%BB%E5%85%A8%E7%89%9B%E5%86%8D%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E8%A6%8B%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA-%E5%B7%B2%E6%AD%A3%E5%BC%8F%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B%E5%B0%87%E7%95%B6%E4%BA%8B%E4%BA%BA%E7%A7%BB%E9%80%81%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n12 名港人上月疑潛逃台灣時被中國海警截獲，至今被關押在深圳鹽田看守所已經第 27 日。受其中一名港人黃偉然家屬委託的內地律師任全牛，今早持看守所早前要求的「公證書」，再度要求會見當事人被拒，並獲告知當事人已委託另外兩名律師，相信是官派律師。截至目前為止，至少已有三名港人被當局以獲官派律師為由，拒絕會見家人委派的律師。<br />\n<br />\n任全牛今早再赴鹽田公安局遞交公證委託手續，鹽田公安分局法制科一位姓李的女警官接收委託手續文件，當時聲稱會盡快轉交給辦案人，並要求律師聯繫通知表上一名莊姓警官。<br />\n<br />\n任全牛其後前往鹽田看守所要求預約會見當事人，看守所卻表示其當事人已有兩名律師。任全牛指出看守所與辦案單位說法不符，辦案單位無表示當事人已另有律師。看守所則僅要求任全牛聯絡鹽田公安分局、案件經辦人莊明俊警官，並拒絕提供兩名相信是官派律師的姓名。<br />\n<br />\n莊明俊其後致電任全牛，要求在鹽田公安分局見面，但任全牛到公安分局後，莊明俊沒有現時，公安分局的李姓女警官將委託手續交還任全牛，並重申當事人已委託另外兩名律師。<br />\n<br />\n律師申請爭議鹽田管轄權 要求移送返港<br />\n<br />\n任全牛今日向公安分局提交一份「刑事管轄權異議移送申請書」，爭議鹽田公安分局對本案無管轄權，正式要求辦案單位將當事人移送回香港。<br />\n<br />\n任全牛今日亦向鹽田檢察院控告鹽田公安分局，指公安分局違法剝奪當事人辯護權，拒絕告知其當事人兩名官派律師的姓名及電話。據悉，檢察院至今未派員正式接收控告書。<br />\n<br />\n多名受家屬委託的內地律師，早前分別前往鹽田看守所要求會見當事人被拒，鹽田當局要求律師就家屬委託關係進行「公證」手續。但直至目前，至少三名具名、持公證書的內地律師，包括任全牛、盧思位及紀中久，被當局以當事人已委託其他律師為由，拒絕會見，相信是被委派了官派律師。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/E6AA94E6A188_0012028129_KZeEX_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2FE6AA94E6A188_0012028129_KZeEX_1200x0.png&h=6dcacad9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8bb803c1eeb677474b626b4c82204545759509ba","tid":2208433,"uid":54337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:11:37.000Z","msg":"9月7日入申請書<br />\n而家9月19日了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/disappointed.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37452da3f42a8b29a8f0de9d936dec04caf3cd25","tid":2208433,"uid":93962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:12:08.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"039efa6eb02c0c6ae5362e8304092bdc1e980714","tid":2208433,"uid":362121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:13:54.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/playing-life.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fplaying-life.jpg&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCp1e7EkIXHZyG33jvsgDPMQ%3D&h=f2433828\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/playing-life.jpg</a>"},{"pid":"d721e5474dd0516ca69b21137c97b10955e4e0b5","tid":2208433,"uid":362121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T02:15:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2015/11/playing-life.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F11%2Fplaying-life.jpg&h=10a918aa&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}